msgctxt "sn40.8:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 40 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 40 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn40.8:0.2"
msgid "1. Moggallānavagga "
msgstr "1. By Moggallāna "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn40.8:0.3"
msgid "8. Nevasaññānāsaññāyatanapañhāsutta "
msgstr "8. A Question About the Dimension of Neither Perception Nor Non-Perception "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn40.8:1.1"
msgid "“‘Nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ, nevasaññānāsaññāyatanan’ti vuccati. "
msgstr "“They speak of this thing called the ‘dimension of neither perception nor non-perception’. "

msgctxt "sn40.8:1.2"
msgid "Katamaṃ nu kho nevasaññānāsaññāyatananti? "
msgstr "What is the dimension of neither perception nor non-perception? "

msgctxt "sn40.8:1.3"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, āvuso, etadahosi: "
msgstr "It occurred to me: "

msgctxt "sn40.8:1.4"
msgid "‘idha bhikkhu sabbaso ākiñcaññāyatanaṃ samatikkamma nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ upasampajja viharati. "
msgstr "‘It’s when a mendicant, going totally beyond the dimension of nothingness, enters and remains in the dimension of neither perception nor non-perception. "

msgctxt "sn40.8:1.5"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati nevasaññānāsaññāyatanan’ti. "
msgstr "This is called the dimension of neither perception nor non-perception.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn40.8:1.6"
msgid "So khvāhaṃ, āvuso, sabbaso ākiñcaññāyatanaṃ samatikkamma nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ upasampajja viharāmi. "
msgstr "And so … I was entering and remaining in the dimension of neither perception nor non-perception. "

msgctxt "sn40.8:1.7"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, āvuso, iminā vihārena viharato ākiñcaññāyatanasahagatā saññāmanasikārā samudācaranti. "
msgstr "While I was in that meditation, perceptions and attentions accompanied by the dimension of nothingness beset me. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn40.8:2.1"
msgid "Atha kho maṃ, āvuso, bhagavā iddhiyā upasaṅkamitvā etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then the Buddha came up to me with his psychic power and said, "

msgctxt "sn40.8:2.2"
msgid "‘moggallāna, moggallāna. "
msgstr "‘Moggallāna, Moggallāna! "

msgctxt "sn40.8:2.3"
msgid "Mā, brāhmaṇa, nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ pamādo, nevasaññānāsaññāyatane cittaṃ saṇṭhapehi, nevasaññānāsaññāyatane cittaṃ ekodiṃ karohi, nevasaññānāsaññāyatane cittaṃ samādahā’ti. "
msgstr "Don’t neglect the dimension of neither perception nor non-perception, brahmin! Settle your mind in the dimension of neither perception nor non-perception; unify your mind and immerse it in the dimension of neither perception nor non-perception.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn40.8:2.4"
msgid "So khvāhaṃ, āvuso, aparena samayena sabbaso ākiñcaññāyatanaṃ samatikkamma nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ upasampajja vihāsiṃ. "
msgstr "And so, after some time … I entered and remained in the dimension of neither perception nor non-perception. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn40.8:2.5"
msgid "Yañhi taṃ, āvuso, sammā vadamāno vadeyya … pe … mahābhiññataṃ patto”ti. "
msgstr "So if anyone should be rightly called a disciple who attained to great direct knowledge with help from the Teacher, it’s me.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn40.8:2.6"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

